{"tid":1442332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好失焦，要贏一定打721同鄉黑勾結","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:26:43.000Z","uid":276632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecff979538acaf40a2f9380928c9ac51830046d","tid":1442332,"uid":276632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"我親戚收到黑警資料，已混了批便裝同福建幫著黑衣圍警局同做更過激行為，包括縱火燒店<br />\n大家要對焦目標，先針對無差別打人而無執法，呢個位係最傷香港人死穴，<br />\n專攻鄉黑警同律政司勾結<br />\n中間同淺藍係拉攏對象，再浪費勇士被犬拉，只會浪費很多時間同資源，又失焦<br />\n<br />\n最後文宣要簡化呢張圖，加埋外國走資，盡量廣傳<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOetSq7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOetSq7.png&h=b5c2c64c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"521b9adaf78262179d4b797f233b7b4275c155e7","tid":1442332,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勁推推推推推推推推推三千次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解元朗我地會入去屌鳩班鄉黑<br />\n北角就要驚班陸佬先？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解要我地取消遊行 ，放低尊嚴，去避班大陸撚？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76e1a88107bab87909b935d3148d7947ed2088a0","tid":1442332,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d963fc18d234d27afa6963f6b12d37e591b2f1c","tid":1442332,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"劇本編好啦,一個都唔檢控"},{"pid":"174577ff8434ff55be43ee5c92cfe388661887cc","tid":1442332,"uid":10201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"857c8d1c84e1d3a5967872d841c2862cc766e75b","tid":1442332,"uid":20444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed2cfb5ab95e1cd474c287ec87fe513fd85f2e8","tid":1442332,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1a1d52624a4316a3becd0b30b0de5c3a332d68e","tid":1442332,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}